description: Ideally located where East Broadway meets West Broadway, this condo-quality, three-family consists of nine massive bedrooms and 7 full bathrooms. Each unit is fully equipped with hardwood floors, marble bathrooms, mini-split air condition systems in each bedroom, in-unit laundry, high ceilings, stainless steel appliances and custom cabinets. Each unit is expansive with an open layout, totaling over 4,224 square feet. Apartment One is a duplex apartment, and Apartment Two and Three each span one floor.   The location of this building is unbeatable, with the MBTA 9 and 10 bus just feet away, and the MBTA Redline Broadway Train stop a twelve-minute walk away. This building benefits from being situated in one of Boston’s fastest growing and diverse submarkets.
